{"tid":2150674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"咁鍾意challenge 不如整個appledailychallenge?! 今個月日日都買一份蘋果g持","createTime":"2020-08-11T04:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:19:56.000Z","uid":4322,"like":128,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ac154881d98e9ae3ef5de8bf61367e65625676","tid":2150674,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"個challenge好簡單 每日買完蘋果再hashtag 一個月為期 有多無少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺上Facebook/ig/Twitter (twitter緊要d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n#appledailychallenge <br />\n#freejimmylai<br />\n記得tag多幾個fd子日日互相提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thYi955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthYi955.jpg&h=45ab38e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上既野做到就做！<br />\n<br />\n坦白講 一個月日日一份蘋果講緊都係300左右<br />\n香港地食餐好少少既dinner都唔止呢個數<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>但可以話畀全世界知我地香港人仲好需要蘋果</strong></span></span><br />\n呢個月日日買一份 有錢就買多幾份派又好送畀人又好<br />\n<br />\n而蘋果動/壹仔要訂都訂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 邊度仲有蘋果賣 樓下去左幾間都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3229fec76d8293f2d9e3dab922b7bcb140745ff8","tid":2150674,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"b3eb91bd9d030b48466d6e6c1dcf51dc58256878","tid":2150674,"uid":226471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53b582d2474241eb76bd429b08889f76fb2179ff","tid":2150674,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r